    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Spencer's Retail - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "Spencer's Retail invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Marketplace Manager at our Kanpur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Spencer's Retail:\nSpencer's Retail is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Spencer's Retail!",
